<p><a name="References" id="References"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Externality&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.auburn.edu/~johnspm/gloss/externality" class="external text" title="http://www.auburn.edu/~johnspm/gloss/externality" rel="nofollow">Definition</a></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREF.5B.5BArthur_Cecil_Pigou.7CPigou.2C_A.C..5D.5D1920"><a href="/wiki/Arthur_Cecil_Pigou" title="Arthur Cecil Pigou">Pigou, A.C.</a> (1920). <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Economics_of_Welfare&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Economics of Welfare (page does not exist)">Economics of Welfare</a></i>. <a href="/wiki/Macmillan_and_Co." title="Macmillan and Co." class="mw-redirect">Macmillan and Co.</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=%5B%5BEconomics+of+Welfare%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BArthur+Cecil+Pigou%7CPigou%2C+A.C.%5D%5D&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BArthur+Cecil+Pigou%7CPigou%2C+A.C.%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=1920&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BMacmillan+and+Co.%5D%5D&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Externality"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li>Baumol, W.J. (1972), ‘On Taxation and the Control of Externalities’, <i>American Economic Review</i>, <i>62</i>(3), 307-322.</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREF.5B.5BGordon_Tullock.7CTullock.2C_G..5D.5D2005"><a href="/wiki/Gordon_Tullock" title="Gordon Tullock">Tullock, G.</a> (2005). <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Public_Goods,_Redistribution_and_Rent_Seeking&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Public Goods, Redistribution and Rent Seeking (page does not exist)">Public Goods, Redistribution and Rent Seeking</a></i>. <a href="/w/index.php?title=Edward_Elgar_Publishing,_Inc.&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Edward Elgar Publishing, Inc. (page does not exist)">Edward Elgar Publishing, Inc.</a>. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/184376637X" class="internal">ISBN 1-84376-637-X</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=%5B%5BPublic+Goods%2C+Redistribution+and+Rent+Seeking%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BGordon+Tullock%7CTullock%2C+G.%5D%5D&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BGordon+Tullock%7CTullock%2C+G.%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BEdward+Elgar+Publishing%2C+Inc.%5D%5D&amp;rft.isbn=1-84376-637-X&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Externality"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
